The previous generation 
of digital asset security
In this section, we’ll walk you through the previous generation of security 
technologies that were utilized to protect digital assets. These technologies were 
widely utilized in earlier attempts at protecting digital assets. However, they are no 
longer able to support the operational and security needs of today’s digital asset 
businesses, and they provided the foundation upon which today’s next-generation 
systems were built.
Fireblocks’ Multi-layer Philosophy for Securing Digital Assets
